{"tid":2241726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年年半價換購新機! 蘋果香港將推 iPhone Upgrade Program","createTime":"2020-10-13T13:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T15:37:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"34cbd067c543cbfbf3a01a4e9c49008069e34826","tid":2241726,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2774195/sm1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2774195%2Fsm1_600.jpg&h=612aa885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n智能手機市場競爭激烈，手機生產商需要各出奇謀才可以留客。蘋果公司（Apple Inc）早已於美國、中國兩地推出「iPhone 年年換新計劃」（iPhone Upgrade Program ），讓用戶低至半價升級新 iPhone。最近有消息指，香港或會推出此計劃。<br />\n<br />\n在蘋果 iPhone 12 即將上市之際，根據外媒報道指，蘋果公司早於今年 4 月，就在在香港申請「iPhone for Life」的商標專利，專利編號為 305380876。報道指，此專利包含零售服務等的 35 類項目，以及包含金融相關的 36 類項目。有分析預計，該商標專利其實為 iPhone 年年換新計劃（iPhone Upgrade Program ）。<br />\n<br />\n「iPhone 年年換新計劃」是蘋果公司在 2015 年於美國推出的計劃，目的是吸引舊用戶購買新機。用戶只要在 Apple Store 實體店購買 iPhone 時，即時加購 AppleCare+ 計畫，就可以在購買該手機後的第 10 個月起到第 13 個月底內，以原有手機零售價格 50% 的折扣額優惠，升級換購新 iPhone，但用戶需要把舊手機退回蘋果。因此，以 iPhone 的高保持情況看，此計劃未必有著數。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2774195?r=mcsdfbez?=r1&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2774195%3Fr%3Dmcsdfbez%3F%3Dr1%26&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbaWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=c1062283\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2774195?r=mcsdfbez?=r1&amp;</a>"},{"pid":"645f35d6a96daa44020d1b9b9176983ef1beb4f6","tid":2241726,"uid":123696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"乜撚叫 高保持狀況<br />\n<br />\n文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f408ce9d49ab5bc4a8ba79910d7ec718c3f0f05c","tid":2241726,"uid":13065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:41:54.000Z","msg":